query:
UPDATE rexecutor_jobs SET
                status = $2,
                data = $3,
                attempt = $4,
                max_attempts = $5,
                errors = $6,
                scheduled_at = $7,
                attempted_at = $8,
                completed_at = $9,
                cancelled_at = $10,
                discarded_at = $11
            WHERE id = $1
